Alexander F. Stern 
Executive Compensation
As Chief Operating Officer and Chief Executive Officer, Financial Advisory at LAZARD LTD, Alexander F. Stern  made $6,937,086 in total compensation.  Of this total $750,000 was received as a salary, $2,050,000 was received as a bonus, $0 was received in stock options, $4,101,277 was awarded as stock and $35,809 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


