Alexander F. Stern

COO of Lazard and CEO of Financial Advisory






Alexander F. Stern, age 50, has served as Chief Operating Officer of Lazard Ltd and Lazard Group since November 2008, and has been the Chief Executive Officer of Financial Advisory since April 2015. He has served as a Managing Director since January 2002 and as the Firm's Global Head of Strategy since February 2006. Mr. Stern previously served as a Vice President in Lazard's Financial Advisory business from January 1998 to December 2000 and as a Director from January 2001 to December 2001. Mr. Stern joined Lazard in 1994 and previously held various positions with Patricof & Co. Ventures and IBM.






























